snippet.title: Immortal Sins Extended Demo #1 (v2)
snippet.description:
A small demo of the updated UI, a few of the mechanics, shop interaction, and a small tour of the menus.

The video was taken from a development build.

The demo of the game (Disc 1) can be downloaded from here:
https://aceofaces-mod.tumblr.com/immortal-sins
